## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/includes/deprecatedcontent-md.md)]  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6de0f-102"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity> consente di impostare lo stato dall'applicazione host.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6de0f-102">The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity> allows for setting the state from the host application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6de0f-103">Questo consente all'applicazione host di eseguire l'override dello stato corrente di una macchina a stati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6de0f-103">This enables the host application to override the current state of a state machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6de0f-104">Può essere ottenuto accodando un'istanza della classe <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SetStateEventArgs> all'oggetto WorkflowQueue denominato dalla costante <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity.SetStateQueueName?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6de0f-104">This can be accomplished by enqueuing an instance of the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SetStateEventArgs> class to the WorkflowQueue named by the constant <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity.SetStateQueueName?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6de0f-105">Un metodo più semplice per ottenere questo risultato è di utilizzare il metodo <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> nella classe <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6de0f-105">A simpler way to accomplish this is to use the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> method in the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6de0f-106">È possibile utilizzare il metodo <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> per eseguire un'operazione SetState dell'host o direttamente accodando un evento al flusso di lavoro della macchina a stati come illustrato nell'esempio seguente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6de0f-106">You can use the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> method to perform a SetState operation from the host, or you can do it yourself by enqueuing an event to the state machine workflow as shown in the following example.</span></span>  
  
```  
public void SetState(string targetStateName)  
{  
      if (targetStateName == null)  
      {  
            throw new ArgumentNullException("targetStateName");  
      }  
      SetStateEventArgs args1 = new SetStateEventArgs(targetStateName);  
      this.WorkflowInstance.EnqueueItemOnIdle("SetStateQueue", args1, null, null);  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6de0f-107">Per attendere questi eventi speciali, il flusso di lavoro della macchina a stati utilizza una coda speciale chiamata `SetStateQueue`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6de0f-107">The state machine workflow uses a special queue called `SetStateQueue` to listen to these special events.</span></span>
